  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">来了，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Gemini 3 Pro</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">已经可以在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Google AI Studio</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上体验，免费。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不废话，直接看实测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">1）复刻网站</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是B站。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi502fnk11ln\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239310\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 9px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cc20ac6a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCibsWkvknibHkz7oOAElo46WxTcGUrd6h6pAevjxpxfS2dycb5fLv8qM0iaiaRkUdZ0eEuc98uRZY53EA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">输入Prompt：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">帮我复刻这个网站。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是哈基米3生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi502kzg14f0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239311\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.637962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 9px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6851ab23&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCibsWkvknibHkz7oOAElo46WxFUjRYnqgWYcMFkkSNwM9TWq0Bob2mZTI3icuWvmPnwTQeX4Tyyiaw9hQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">几乎</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">像素级复刻。不注意，我还以为进了一个假的B站。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">注意看这些细节，圆角卡片、悬停效果、视频封面上的数据遮罩层，几乎一模一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi50c5fc1yry\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239312\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4351851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 9px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=de3a059a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCibsWkvknibHkz7oOAElo46WxkLJzbgL2aAvjkfibdj5UmcZMAVULoUF43FtuuBeSxvibzZvy9l8GJMOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">2）信息卡片</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">信息卡片，几个国产模型我都用过，总觉得还差点意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">要么不会错位排版，要么处理不好中英文、大小字的结合，要么容易出现内容溢出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gemini 3 Pro这效果，是我目前测试过的多个coding模型里效果最好的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi50cbsk1048\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239313\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.511111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 9px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db29ca35&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCibsWkvknibHkz7oOAElo46Wxo3OibThZDRK3hbNLpyWbRibF2BuM8iaA93zgBog8JQA47alibJ9nWyPBuA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">完整的Prompt是：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">提炼下面的内容生成一个HTML网页。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">内容全文：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">{</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">内容</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">}</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">具体要求如下：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1.视觉设计：采用{Magazine Layout}风格布局，{深色}主题色，营造现代高端氛围。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2.字体与排版：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">·使用超大字体或数字突出核心要点，中文采用大号粗体，强调视觉冲击力。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">·英文使用小号字体作为点缀，与中文形成比例反差，提升设计层次感。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3视觉元素：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">·融入超大视觉元素（如标题、背景图或装饰）以突出重点，与小型元素形成强烈对比。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">·使用简洁的勾线风格图形作为数据可视化或配图元素，保持现代感和清晰度。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">4.色彩与效果：运用高亮色（单色透明度渐变）营造科技感，每种高亮色独立使用，避免不同高亮色之间的渐变混杂。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">5.技术要求：引入专业图标库（如Font Awesome或Material Icons，通过CDN加载），避免使用emoji作为主要图标。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">6.内容要求：提炼内容关键要点，不忽略重要细节。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">7.尺寸：内容在{1200*1800}区域内完成完整展示（不需要缩放也能完整显示），内容以中文为主展示。</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">3）N-Back实验</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Prompt来自@刘聪，我调整了一下汉字。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">你需要实现一个N-Back实验页面。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">N-Back实验的原理是，每隔1s闪烁一张图片，让用户判断当前的图片与前面第N张图片是否一致，一致选择是，不一致选择否。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">其中，图片为常见的10个中文汉字，[</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"人\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"工\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"智\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"能\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"是\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"新\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"质\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"生\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"产\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"力\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">]</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">界面需要每次开始时，选N的值，选择为2，3，4，三种。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">需要用户点击30次，也就是不同N值时展现的图片个数不同，例如N=2，则需要32张图片，当第三张出现时，提醒用户开始点击。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">你需要记录两个内容，一个是用户点击是否准确，一个是出现图像到用户点击之间的时间，最后给出点击准确率和反应时间。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">注意：图片展示只有15次是N-back正确内容，防止实验过难或过于简单。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">实验过程，如果正确让用户点击“A”键，错误让用户点击“L”键。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">同时界面必须符合现代审美，实验结果可以导出下载。</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同样一次直出，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">审美、逻辑均在线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">4）象限图</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Prompt是：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">搜索GPT、Claude、Gemini、GLM、Kimi、DeepSeek、Qwen等模型在2025年的发布情况。然后创建一个象限图html，用来展示这些模型厂商在「模型能力」「开放程度」「商业化情况」「创新性」四个维度的分布。</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gemini 3 Pro的搜索能力稍弱了点，几个模型都没有get到最新的信息，包括他们家自己的模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi50cklx1eix\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239329\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9541015625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 9px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=59a928e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCibsWkvknibHkz7oOAElo46WxlymAIk0QicVlZmLuicnNtES0xKaBWX0SHTkT6LbfmP3bu9uBqxzibwOqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这前端设计，依然无敌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mi50crb41y6v\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239330\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8103813559322034\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"944\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 9px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d58aa16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibCibsWkvknibHkz7oOAElo46WxW4XEcpzpoU8oMftwF2G3NMYEjWxGE9wGeOpRuTTsbXvyJluQWhibIUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">5）大模型向量化科普动画</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个case，我们之前在</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMTU5OTQ1Nw==&amp;mid=2653722752&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1a095e0427b7b5f24744626704f9f7ab&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"K2-Thinking\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">K2-Thinking</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">里跑过。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">我想用 Three.js 制作一个完整的可交互 3D 可视化网页，模拟“大语言模型向量空间中的词语查询”。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">页面需求如下，请你直接输出完整、可运行的 HTML + JavaScript 代码：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">核心功能：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">展示一个 3D 坐标空间背景（类似星空或网格地面）。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">每个词语对应一个球体节点，节点上方有标签（中文字）。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">右侧有一个固定的控制面板，围绕“月球”一词列出一组可点击的词语按钮。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">当点击某个词语按钮时：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">中央显示该词对应的球体（例如红色）。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">自动高亮并连线到若干余弦相似度最高的词语（例如 5 个）。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">显示相似度（例如 “余弦相似度：0.89”）在悬浮提示框中。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">支持拖拽旋转、滚轮缩放相机视角。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">显示坐标轴（X/Y/Z）和地面网格。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">动态更新：当点击不同的词语时，中间的球体和连线重新计算显示。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">数据部分：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">请内置一个简化的向量表（用 JSON 数组模拟），每个词语对应一个 3 维向量，如：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">const vectors = {</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">'attention'</span></span><span leaf=\"\">: [0.9, 0.2, 0.5],</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">'model'</span></span><span leaf=\"\">: [0.7, 0.3, 0.4],</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">'knowledge'</span></span><span leaf=\"\">: [0.2, 0.8, 0.5],</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">...</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">};</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">用 JavaScript 函数计算两个向量的余弦相似度。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">视觉要求：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">背景使用深色主题，星空或粒子背景。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">标签悬浮在球体上方。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">球体颜色按类别区分（中心词红色，相似词橙色，其他灰色）。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">附加功能（可选）：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">在左下角显示当前选中词语与最高相似度词语的坐标与相似度。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">自动平滑飞行到目标词语中心（Three.js Camera tween）。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">请输出完整 HTML 文件，使用最新 Three.js CDN 链接，不依赖外部服务。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"line-height:26px;font-style:italic;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mi4zhfzv-rbdniq\" data-topic=\"1\">#Prompt</a>&nbsp;by 弘文</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gemini 3 Pro依旧一次直出，这效果真的太强了。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: